<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="zh-CN">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge,chrome=1" />
  <meta name="format-detection" content="telphone=no" />
  <meta name="format-detection" content="email=no" />
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black" />
  <meta name="screen-orientation" content="portrait" />
  <meta name="x5-orientation" content="320" />
  <meta name="HandheldFriendly" content="true" />
  <meta name="MobileOptimized" content="320" />
  <meta http-equiv="pragma" content="no-cache">
  <meta http-equiv="cache-control" content="no-cache">
  <meta http-equiv="expires" content="0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/common.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css">
  <title>好礼送不停</title>
</head>
<body>  
  <div class="container">
    <div class="topTitle">
      <img src="./images/takeActive/theme.png">
    </div>
    <div class="top">
        <span class="myscore">我的积分:0</span> 
        <span class="changeBtn">点击兑换</span>
    </div>
    <div class="prize_img">
        <img src="./images/takeActive/zhongjian.png">
    </div>
    <!-- 活动参与情况 -->
    <div class="winnerList">
        <div class="winnerBox">
            <ul class="winnerInfo">
                
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div> 
    <!-- 我的中奖信息 -->
    <div class="myInfo">
        <div class="prizeInfo" >
            <img src="./images/takeActive/winnerInfo.png">
        </div>
        <div id="toCheck" >点击查询</div>
        <div class="prizeList">
            <div class="title">
                <span>奖品</span>
                <span>中奖时间</span>
                <span>状态</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="rule">
        <img src="./images/takeActive/rule.png">
    </div>
    <!-- <span id="url"></span> -->
    <div class="toStart">
        <!-- <p class="titleImg"><img src="./images/takeActive/Title.png"></p> -->
        <div class="titleText">
            <div>1.参与活动前请先打开您的电视机，并用i视视APP绑定电信机顶盒，点击查看
                <img class="boundBtn" src="./images/takeActive/boundTips.png">
            </div>
            <div>2.在i视视APP首页左下角点击【电视遥控】</div>
        </div>
        <div class="centerImg" style="text-align: center">
            <img src="./images/takeActive/explain.png">
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="js/jquery-1.11.3.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="./js/startactive.js"></script>
</body>
</html>